sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant BE as Spring Boot
  participant CM as CacheManager
  participant CF as Caffeine Cache
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  C->>BE: GET /category (Bearer JWT)
  BE->>CM: @Cacheable lookup (key: userId)
  CM->>CF: get(userId)
  alt Cache Hit
    CF-->>CM: Cached data
    CM-->>BE: Return cached DTO list
    BE-->>C: 200 OK (no DB query)
  else Cache Miss
    CF-->>CM: null
    CM-->>BE: Proceed to method
    BE->>DB: SELECT * FROM categories WHERE user_id = ?
    DB-->>BE: Category rows
    BE->>BE: Map to DTOs
    BE->>CF: put(userId, dtoList)
    BE-->>C: 200 OK
  end

  Note over C,DB: On any write operation:
  C->>BE: POST /category (create)
  BE->>DB: INSERT INTO categories
  BE->>CM: UserCacheEvictService.evictAllUserCaches(userId)
  CM->>CF: evict categories, habits, tasks, goals, routines, schedules, todayRoutine
  BE-->>C: 200 OK
